name: With No Help
description:
With No Help  is a bullet hell, teleport around, shoot-em-up made by myself and a friend over a weekend . Click to shoot, WASD to move, R to reload the game and Esc to Exit

The Teleporters take a second to warm up :)

UnZip the file to any folder you like and click "With No Help" to run the game

Happy Gaming 

Alex and Jack
